	djn@pkns.com, jfrizzell@gibbs-bruns.com, mlk@pkns.com,
	mmolland@brobeck.com, msmith1@enron.com, pmeringolo@brobeck.com,
	richard.b.sanders@enron.com, robert.c.williams@enron.com,
	sbishop@gibbs-bruns.com
Subject: FW: Enron: Response to Criminal Charges
Mime-Version: 1.0
