X-From: Fergus, Gary S.  <GFergus@brobeck.com>
X-To: Amanda Smith  <ADSmith@brobeck.com>, Andy Pickens (E-mail)  <apickens@gibbs-bruns.com>, Barrett H. Reasoner (E-mail)  <breasoner@gibbs-bruns.com>, David J. Noonan (E-mail)  <djn@pkns.com>, Jean Frizzell (E-mail)  <jfrizzell@gibbs-bruns.com>, Michael L. Kirby (E-mail)  <mlk@pkns.com>, Michael Molland  <MMolland@brobeck.com>, Mike D. Smith (E-mail)  <msmith1@enron.com>, Peter Meringolo  <PMeringolo@brobeck.com>, Richard B. Sanders Esq. (E-mail)  <richard.b.sanders@enron.com>, Robert C. Williams (E-mail)  <Robert.C.Williams@enron.com>, Susan Bisop (E-mail)  <sbishop@gibbs-bruns.com>
