Subject: Status report on document identification at Enron Corp. offices i n
 San Francisco
Cc: smith@enron.com, adsmith@brobeck.com, meringolo@enron.com,
	pmeringolo@brobeck.com
Mime-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=us-ascii
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 7bit
Bcc: smith@enron.com, adsmith@brobeck.com, meringolo@enron.com,
	pmeringolo@brobeck.com
X-From: "Molland, Michael E." <MMolland@brobeck.com>@ENRON <IMCEANOTES-+22Molland+2C+20Michael+20E+2E+22+20+3CMMolland+40brobeck+2Ecom+3E+40ENRON@ENRON.com>
X-To: Williams, Robert C. </O=ENRON/OU=NA/CN=RECIPIENTS/CN=RWILLIA2>, Sanders, Richard B. </O=ENRON/OU=NA/CN=RECIPIENTS/CN=RSANDER>, 'sbishop@gibbs-bruns.com', 'mlk@pkns.com', 'mtuohey@velaw.com', Fergus, Gary S. <GFergus@brobeck.com>
X-cc: Smith, Amanda D. <ADSmith@brobeck.com>, Meringolo, Peter <PMeringolo@brobeck.com>
