From MAILER-DAEMON Mon Apr 18 14:25:46 2022
Message-ID: <5948084.1075858668674.JavaMail.evans@thyme>
Date: Wed, 27 Jun 2001 18:01:41 -0700 (PDT)
From: mmolland@brobeck.com
To: c..williams@enron.com
Subject: Discussion of document retention policy for EES
Cc: b..sanders@enron.com
Mime-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=us-ascii
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 7bit
Bcc: b..sanders@enron.com
X-From: "Molland, Michael E." <MMolland@brobeck.com>@ENRON <IMCEANOTES-+22Molland+2C+20Michael+20E+2E+22+20+3CMMolland+40brobeck+2Ecom+3E+40ENRON@ENRON.com>
X-To: Williams, Robert C. </O=ENRON/OU=NA/CN=RECIPIENTS/CN=RWILLIA2>
X-cc: Sanders, Richard B. </O=ENRON/OU=NA/CN=RECIPIENTS/CN=RSANDER>, 'mlk@pkns.com', 'sbishop@gibbs-bruns.com', 'mtuohey@velaw.com', Fergus, Gary S. <GFergus@brobeck.com>
