 -----Original Message-----
From: 	"Molland, Michael E." <MMolland@brobeck.com>@ENRON [mailto:IMCEANOTES-+22Molland+2C+20Michael+20E+2E+22+20+3CMMolland+40brobeck+2Ecom+3E+40ENRON@ENRON.com] 
